@@TJvValidateEditDisplayFormat
<TITLE TJvValidateEditDisplayFormat type>
Summary
  Defines available display formats.
Description
  TJvValidateEditDisplayFormat is used as the type for the DisplayFormat property in TJvValidateEdit.
  Changing DisplayFormat might change the Alignment of the text if AutoAlignment is true and the prefix
  or suffix used when the control doesn't have focus.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
