  Only displays characters A-Z, a-z.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvValidateEditDisplayFormat.dfAlphaNumeric
  Only displays characters A-Z, a-z, 0-9.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvValidateEditDisplayFormat.dfBinary
  Only displays binary characters (0,1).

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvValidateEditDisplayFormat.dfCheckChars
  Only displays characters in CheckCars.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvValidateEditDisplayFormat.dfCurrency
  Only displays currency characters (0-9, decimal).

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvValidateEditDisplayFormat.dfCustom
  Only displays characters where OnCustomValidate sets IsValid to true.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvValidateEditDisplayFormat.dfFloat
  Only displays float characters (0-9, decimal).

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvValidateEditDisplayFormat.dfHex
  Only displays hexadecimal characters (0-9,A-F,a-f).

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvValidateEditDisplayFormat.dfInteger
  Only displays integer characters (0-9).

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvValidateEditDisplayFormat.dfNonCheckChars
  Only displays chacraters not in CheckCars.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvValidateEditDisplayFormat.dfNone
  Displays any character.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvValidateEditDisplayFormat.dfOctal
  Only displays octal characters (0-7).

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvValidateEditDisplayFormat.dfPercent
  Only displays percentage characters (0-9).

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvValidateEditDisplayFormat.dfScientific
